stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> HoodOff : wanted = IDLE

    [*] --> Moving : wanted = AIMING [not at setpoint]
    [*] --> HoodAtSetpoint : wanted = AIMING [at setpoint]

    [*] --> Zeroing : wanted = DUCKED

    Moving --> HoodAtSetpoint : position within 1 deg tolerance
    HoodAtSetpoint --> Moving : position drifts outside tolerance

    note right of HoodOff
        Motor output: zero.
    end note

    note right of Moving
        PID position control.
        Aggressive near center,
        smooth near soft limits.
    end note

    note right of HoodAtSetpoint
        Holding target angle.
        Signals shooter readiness.
    end note

    note right of Zeroing
        Moving hood to 0 degrees.
        Smooth position control.
    end note
